description: Add filename to error message when we're unable to stat local filename (`issue 795 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/795>`__)
Fix response parsing for the ``aws s3api get-bucket-policy`` command (`issue 678 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/678>`__)
Fix bug when specifying profiles that don't exist in the CLI config file (`issue botocore 294 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/294>`__)
Handle Amazon S3 error responses that have a 200 OK status code (`issue botocore 298 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/298>`__)
Update the ``aws sts`` command to the latest version
Update the ``aws cloudsearch`` command to the latest version
